 Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132032379,imgsize-98994.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: California security guard fires Taser into man's face at point-blank range, arrested]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132030077.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[In a shocking incident outside a Carlsbad bar during a soccer watch party, a security guard has been charged after reportedly tasering a man in the face. The altercation was captured on video, revealing the man collapsing following the shock. Police have arrested 42-year-old David Marquez on charges of assault with a deadly weapon and stun gun assault. The victim is receiving medical care, and investigations are still underway.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-california-security-guard-fires-taser-into-mans-face-at-point-blank-range-arrested/articleshow/132030077.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-california-security-guard-fires-taser-into-mans-face-at-point-blank-range-arrested/articleshow/132030077.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-27T12:43:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132030239,imgsize-16956829.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[South Korea scrambles fighter jets as Chinese, Russian warplanes enter air defence zone]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132029546.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-scrambles-fighter-jets-as-chinese-russian-warplanes-enter-air-defence-zone/articleshow/132029546.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[htt